title: The Weaks - Converse Rubber Tracks Live
description:
www.converse-music.com

Fresh studio experience turned out to be the start of a hot streak for the Weaks - after being chosen by fellow DIY-punks Joyce Manor to perform with them at a Converse Rubber Tracks Live show at Music Hall of Williamsburg in January, the band was selected by Brand New to come along on a national tour. The Weaks are wasting no time seizing the moment - a debut album, Bad Year, is out April 7th on Lame-O Records.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse-music.com/

Special thanks to:
Big Mama's Warehouse
The Bowery Presents brings you The Music Hall of Williamsburg
